{"tid":621034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳瀅接受「地盤佬」追求","createTime":"2018-04-08T03:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T13:46:12.000Z","uid":81569,"like":10,"dislike":287,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"60e2b79e156200f49ddfc3e044853e29964a30ac","tid":621034,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"陳瀅、傅嘉莉（Kelly）與劉江等，前晚出席「築．動．愛」記者會。陳瀅透露拍攝節目時撞正黑雨，地盤充斥泥濘，恍如山泥傾瀉般，令她一步一驚心。與劉江飾演兩父女的她大讚對方專業，不但自己的對白一字不漏，連她的部分也全背了，劉老師更在合照時笑說：「才剛拍完又掛住我喇！」笑爆全場！<br />\n問到會否接受「地盤佬」的追求？陳瀅坦言不介意，皆因自己也愛吃「地盤佬飯」，例如豆腐火腩飯，故雙方在口味上有共通點。<br />\n另外，經常與富豪傳緋聞的Kelly，亦不抗拒與建造業人士拍拖，她說：「我也有個男生朋友做科文，薪水很好又不危險，其實從事建造業比做藝人的收入更穩定，如果靚仔就更好啦！」"},{"pid":"cfdf2b7a09efc38b557927d863dff033317acb6b","tid":621034,"uid":38744,"like":797,"dislike":4,"score":793,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"D女人呀，好撚古惑架"},{"pid":"3912d793d810bf65df921c9ed2baea81475b5cf9","tid":621034,"uid":57409,"like":332,"dislike":2,"score":330,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"晒鳩氣啦屌"},{"pid":"1b56c404eba4c8dc1d53bad365352fb02d103641","tid":621034,"uid":8048,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"9754371ab9d5e1052bdb1e9da834d579d385e1fd","tid":621034,"uid":50740,"like":135,"dislike":5,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"我也有個男生朋友做科文，薪水很好又不危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56380d29d4fd9f2f6adc28b0d9bf0983bd037e97","tid":621034,"uid":555,"like":22,"dislike":41,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"陳瀅真係正到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00534df7011a6c07a9c2e6ced67e6200cfcbe70a","tid":621034,"uid":71676,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"偽人收檔吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4975c06